In the ESTATE OF Zaneta WALTERS, Robert Walters and Sandi Heter, Objectors-Appellants,
v.
Shirley Shirley and Richard Walters, Co-Executors-Appellees. No. 18-0612 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 15, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Objectors appeal the district court's ruling on their objection to the co-executors' final report. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
